+# Part 9.1 — VisPy Cell Lens Viewer
+
+Part 9.1 adds the first desktop viewer boundary for the cell lens.
+
+## Added
+
+- Renderer-neutral health mapping.
+- Renderer-neutral projection points.
+- Optional VisPy desktop tool.
+- Tests for health/projection logic without requiring VisPy.
+- Rule tests ensuring VisPy is confined to the tool boundary.
+
+## Not added
+
+- No real observation recorder consumer.
+- No mobile SSE.
+- No command path.
+- No optimization loop.
